query:
SELECT (
                COUNT(*) = 0 AND
                (
                    SELECT (miniblocks.pubdata_type != 'Rollup')
                    FROM miniblocks
                    WHERE miniblocks.l1_batch_number = $1
                    ORDER BY miniblocks.number
                    LIMIT 1
                )
            ) AS "da_is_missing!"
            FROM data_availability
            WHERE l1_batch_number = $1
